<L>__{exterior river day.}
<A>__{on a flatbed, stamp paid crosses the river with sethe, her baby and the two boys.}
<L>__{exterior opposite river bank day.}
<A>__{stamp paid helps sethe walk up a very steep bank while the boy without a jacket, carries the baby who wears it.}
<L>__{interior brush covered hutch day.}
<A>__{stamp paid leads sethe and the others into the hutch.}
<C>__{stamp paid}
<D>__{wait here. somebody be here directly. don't move. they'll find you.}
<C>__{sethe}
<D>__{thank you. what's your name so i can remember you right.}
