<A>__{she nods as he and the boys exit.}
<T>__{lap dissolve:}
<A>__{later same location: sethe is asleep with the baby when ella enters the hutch;}
<C>__{ellla}
<D>__{saw the sign a while ago but i couldn't get here no quicker.}
<C>__{sethe}
<D>__{what sign?}
<C>__{ella}
<D>__{stamp always leave the old sty open when there's a crossing. knots a white rag on the post if it's a child too.}
<P>__{(kneels)}
<D>__{my name's ella..where you headed?}
